A mommy first, a bombshell immediately after and a visionary/innovator immediately after that 🤷🏾‍♀️ I have always had this strong desire to go outside the norm of things. A desire to help people. I feel like I fulfill that desire through hair. 

I been getting asked a lot lately what made me start a wig rental business. Well here’s what did it. I like creative things, I love color and I love to see people in different styles and textures, they always look like a new person. I felt like a lot of women were nervous about investing into different styles outside of their normal bone straight or bodywave. Many women play it safe because they don’t wanna spend bands on a color or cut they most likely would want to try first. I also learn that many women do wanna step outside the normal day to day and try different styles but are very indecisive when it comes options.

So doing wig rentals allows me to hone in on more creative and bolder style options. Of course we provide the everyday but we also provide an assortment of wigs for photoshoots, events, and costumes. I wanted to create a whole totally different lane in the hair industry… something that would stand out. I talked to God about it for years with tears in my eyes what could I do… and then one day preparing for this photoshoot in the photo. He gave me the vision…. I didn’t act on it immediately because I wasn’t yet prepared or maybe I was nervous, maybe both. But last year I was literally kicked out of my sleep every night from august till October with dreams of this vision. I started obsessing over it… I really feel that was God saying now or never. Of course I choose now, so here we are… RENT THAT WIG 💕 or buy it brand new at bombshellperfection.com
